<item>
            <title>[LU-11461] Lustre resource agent fails with symlink target</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11461</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If Lustre resource agent is configured with a target device that is a symlink (e.g. &lt;tt&gt;/dev/disk/by-id/scsi-3...&lt;/tt&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The &quot;is mounted&quot; check will fail because findmnt will return the resolved path, which will not match the symlink.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
